E[X|Z]
f_{X.Y}(x,y) = \frac{1}{s\sqrt{2\pi}}\exp(-y^2/2s^2), ~0 \leq x \leq 1, -\infty < y < \infty.
f_{X|Z}(x|z) = \frac{f_{X,Z}(x,z)}{f_Z(z)}  = \frac{f_{X,Z}(x,z)}{\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}f_{X,Z}(x,z)\mathrm dx}.
E[X|Z] = \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} xf_{X|Z}(x|z) \mathrm dx.
f_{X|Z}(x|z) = \frac{f_{Z|X}(z|x)f_X(x)}{f_Z(z)}  = \frac{1}{f_Z(z)}\cdot\frac{1}{s\sqrt{2\pi}}\exp(-(x-z)^2/2s^2),  ~ 0 \leq x \leq 1
